      <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-600">Наши услуги</h2>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Предлагаем профессиональные услуги по уничтожению вредителей с использованием 
        современных технологий и сертифицированных препаратов
      </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Дезинсекция -->
      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-600">Уничтожение насекомых</h3>
        <div class="flex-grow">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <a href="/insects/bedbugs" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Клопы</a>
          <a href="/insects/cockroaches" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Тараканы</a>
          <a href="/insects/fleas" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Блохи</a>
          <a href="/insects/ants" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Муравьи</a>
          <a href="/insects/ticks" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Клещи</a>
          <a href="/insects/mosquitoes" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Комары</a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-neutral-600">Эффективное уничтожение популяций насекомых на любых объектах.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-4">
        <a href="/insects/prices" class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 group-hover:text-green-800 font-medium">
          Узнать цены
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Дератизация -->
      <div class="group bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="bg-green-100 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-green-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" />
        </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-green-600">Уничтожение грызунов</h3>
        <div class="flex-grow">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <a href="/rodents/rats" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Крысы</a>
          <a href="/rodents/mice" class="bg-neutral-100 px-2 py-1 rounded text-sm text-neutral-700 hover:bg-green-100 hover:text-green-700 transition-colors">Мыши</a>
        </div>
